dc_title_s: Tartariae sive magni chami regni typus.
dc_description_s: This is map no. 92 of the author's Theatrvm orbis terrarvm. Antwerpiae, 1584. Cf. U.S. Library of Congress. Division of Maps. A list of geographical atlases in the Library of Congress. 1909-1958. v. 1(no. 388). Text on verso in Latin with signature "92." 1 map; 48 x 35 cm This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
dc_creator_sm: Ortelius, Abraham, 1527-1598.,Plantin, Christophe, approximately 1520-1589, printer.,Dahl, James, former owner.
